Package cs1302.hw.impl

Class MovieTimestamps

java.lang.Object
cs1302.hw.impl.MovieTimestamps
All Implemented Interfaces:
Savable
public class MovieTimestamps extends Object implements Savable
Represents the progress made while watching a movie. Each object stores the user's current place in time, the title of the movie, and its director.
